---
globs: src/presentation/**/routes.ts
alwaysApply: true
---

Define routes as a class, with one route per controller method. Inside the routes definition, instantiate the datasource, repository, and controller.

Configure the database using PrismaClient with the POSTGRES_URL from envs, and create a Prisma adapter (e.g., PrismaPG) to handle database interactions.

The routes class must expose a static method named routes that returns the configured routes.